QuestData.Title: The Admiral's Cabin
QuestData.Description: It's possible we'll find further clues inside the admiral's cabin. You will find it directly below us.$B$BSee if there are any survivors or information that will lead us closer to the World Pillar fragment. Be careful, $n. Whoever got the crew might still be out there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Look for clues in the admiral's cabin of the Alliance Gunship.
QuestData.RewardText: This ship is filled with rats...
